<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Review Reminder - IpTruck</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #ff9800;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .booking-details {
            background-color: #ecf0f1;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .stars {
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .star {
            color: #ffc107;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin: 0 2px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        .review-benefits {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>‚≠ê Review Reminder</h1>
        <p>Help improve our community by sharing your experience</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello <%= companyName %>,</h2>
        
        <p>We hope your recent shipment experience was successful! We'd love to hear about your experience with <%= partnerCompany %>.</p>
        
        <div class="booking-details">
            <h3>üì¶ Booking Details</h3>
            <p><strong>Booking ID:</strong> <%= bookingId %></p>
            <p><strong>Partner:</strong> <%= partnerCompany %></p>
            <p><strong>Delivery Date:</strong> <%= new Date(deliveryDate).toLocaleDateString() %></p>
            <p><strong>Your Role:</strong> <%= userType.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + userType.slice(1) %></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="stars">
            <p>How would you rate your experience?</p>
            <span class="star">‚≠ê</span>
            <span class="star">‚≠ê</span>
            <span class="star">‚≠ê</span>
            <span class="star">‚≠ê</span>
            <span class="star">‚≠ê</span>
        </div>
        
        <center>
            <a href="<%= reviewUrl %>" class="button">Write a Review</a>
        </center>
        
        <div class="review-benefits">
            <h3>üéØ Why Your Review Matters</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Help other users make informed decisions</li>
                <li>Provide valuable feedback to service providers</li>
                <li>Improve the overall quality of our platform</li>
                <li>Build trust within the IpTruck community</li>
                <li>Contribute to better logistics services</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p><strong>üí° Review Tips:</strong></p>
        <ul>
            <li>Be honest and specific about your experience</li>
            <li>Mention timeliness, communication, and service quality</li>
            <li>Include any standout positive or negative aspects</li>
            <li>Keep it constructive and professional</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Your feedback takes just a few minutes but makes a huge difference to our community. Reviews help <%= userType === 'shipper' ? 'carriers' : 'shippers' %> improve their services and help other users choose the right partners.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Already left a review?</strong> Thank you! You can ignore this reminder.</p>
        
        <p><strong>Need Help?</strong></p>
        <p>If you have any questions about the review process, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:support@iptruck.com">support@iptruck.com</a></p>
        
        <p>Thank you for being a valued member of the IpTruck community!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The IpTruck Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>¬© 2024 IpTruck. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p>You received this email because you recently completed a booking.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
